author: Xbox
description:
A sweeping epic returns, told as never before...

FINAL FANTASY TACTICS is one of the most beloved titles in the FINAL FANTASY franchise, known for its rich, character-driven story, exhilarating encounters where strategic positioning and forward planning determine the outcome, and deep character customization featuring numerous jobs and countless combinations of abilities to craft your very own strategies. FINAL FANTASY TACTICS - The Ivalice Chronicles brings the classic strategy RPG to modern consoles with numerous improvements and updates—the best way to experience the title for newcomers and veterans alike!

FINAL FANTASY TACTICS - The Ivalice Chronicles launches Tuesday, September 30th, 2025 for Xbox Series X|S, and is available for pre-order now!

In 1960s Japan, Shimizu Hinako's secluded town of Ebisugaoka is consumed by a sudden fog, transforming her home into a haunting nightmare. Discover a new chapter in the SILENT HILL series, blending psychological horror with a haunting Japanese setting. Will Hinako embrace the beauty hidden within terror, or succumb to the madness that lies ahead?
